title: Wall St climbs as tech rebounds
text:
Wall St climbs as tech rebounds 3:07am IST - 01:20 
Wall Street surged on Thursday, bringing an upbeat end to a tumultuous, holiday-shortened week as tech stocks rebounded. Fred Katayama reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
